    public abstract class AbstractGraphMLReader<G extends Graph,V extends Vertex,E extends Edge>
extends Object
    Abstract class providing basic parsing functionality for graphs stored in the GraphML file format (http://graphml.graphdrawing.org/). This reader does only allow one graph per file!
    Subclasses need to implement the factory methods for creating new graphs, vertices and edges.
